{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.setItem()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage/length\"><code>length</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>removeItem()</code></a></li><li><em><code>setItem()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Storage API 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a> 接口的 <strong><code>setItem()</code></strong> 方法，接受一个键名和值作为参数，将会把键名添加到给定的 <code>Storage</code> 对象中，如果键名已存在，则更新其对应的值。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>storage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>keyName<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> keyValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"keyname\"><code>keyName</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a>，表示要创建或更新的键名。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"keyvalue\"><code>keyValue</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a>，表示要创建或更新的键名对应的值。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"异常","title":"异常","isH3":true,"content":"<p>在存储已满的情况下，调用 <code>setItem()</code> 可能会抛出异常。开发人员应<strong>始终捕获 <code>setItem()</code> 可能抛出的异常</strong>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的函数在本地存储中创建三个数据项。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'red'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Helvetica'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'myCat.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 一个实际的例子：<a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/dom-examples/web-storage/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage Demo</a>。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webstorage.html#dom-storage-setitem-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.Storage.setItem"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Storage.setItem","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\">Storage.getItem()</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\">Storage.removeItem()</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\">使用 Web Storage API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"参数","id":"参数"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Storage 接口的 setItem() 方法，接受一个键名和值作为参数，将会把键名添加到给定的 Storage 对象中，如果键名已存在，则更新其对应的值。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Storage.setItem()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Storage.setItem()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Storage.setItem()","lo